Dear list,
I observed irregular hang-ups when repeatedly performing this code (R  
2.15.0, Windows 7 64, MPICH-II, Rmpi_0.6-2):

<code>

library(Rmpi)
mpi.spawn.Rslaves(nslaves=8)
mpi.close.Rslaves()

</code>

