From simon.urbanek at r-project.org  Thu Dec 13 17:52:23 2012
From: simon.urbanek at r-project.org (Simon Urbanek)
Date: Thu, 13 Dec 2012 11:52:23 -0500
Subject: [R-sig-hpc] recursion depth limitations
